    "The selection and subjective interpretation of marker gene lists also neglect the complex Fig. 6 On the left, scDeepInsight's workflow progresses from inputting the molecular identifier to generating cell annotations.",
    "After processing a reference dataset and query data, they are translated into 2D images, which are used for training the CNN model.",
    "Notably, only the reference data trains the model, while the query set is classified.",
    "For future query sets, the existing model can be directly applied without new training.",
